# WalkWise — API keys.
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your real values, then `npm run build`.
#
# These keys are embedded into the client bundle at build time. Anyone with the
# deployed URL can read them from DevTools and use your quota — only deploy
# this build to audiences you trust, or use restricted/IP-locked keys.
#
# In Vercel, add these in Project Settings → Environment Variables (with the
# VITE_ prefix exactly as below) and redeploy.

VITE_GOOGLE_VISION_API_KEY=
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY= 
VITE_ELEVENLABS_API_KEY= 

# Optional — defaults to "Sarah" if blank.
VITE_ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=EXAVITQu4vr4xnSDxMaL
